title: Rep. Mike Gallager, Stimulus, Vaccines

description:
Guests: Bloomberg News Global Macro Strategist Vincent Cignarella, Rep. Mike Gallager, a Republican representing Wisconsin's 8th congressional district, Dr. Pooja Kumar, Partner at McKinsey & Co, Colin Reed, GOP Strategist and Managing Director at the Levinson Group, Democratic Strategist Joel Payne and Hagar Chemali, CEO of Greenwich Media Strategies and “Host of Oh My World on YouTube!”
